doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='IE=edge')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
    meta(name='description', content='')
    meta(name='author', content='Jacob Burton')
    title foosnet.io

    link(rel="stylesheet" href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.3.0/css/font-awesome.min.css")
    link(href='/vendor/startbootstrap-agency-1.0.4/css/agency.css', rel='stylesheet')
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="/css/marketing.css")

    link(href='//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Kaushan+Script', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Droid+Serif:400,700,400italic,700italic', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='//fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Slab:400,100,300,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

  body#page-top.index

    nav.navbar.navbar-default.navbar-fixed-top
      .container
        .navbar-header.page-scroll
          button.navbar-toggle(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1')
            span.sr-only Toggle navigation
            span.icon-bar
            span.icon-bar
            span.icon-bar
          a.navbar-brand.page-scroll(href='#page-top') foosnet.io

        #bs-example-navbar-collapse-1.collapse.navbar-collapse
          ul.nav.navbar-nav.navbar-right
            li.hidden
              a(href='#page-top')
            li
              a.page-scroll(href='#features') Features
            li
              a.page-scroll(href='#how-it-works') How it works
            li
              a.page-scroll(href='#contact') Contact

    header
      .container
        .intro-text
          .intro-lead-in Welcome to foosnet.io
          .intro-heading Don't just play ... compete!
          a.page-scroll.btn.btn-xl(href='#features') Tell Me More

    section#features
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12.text-center
            h2.section-heading Features
            h3.section-subheading.text-muted Foosball is more fun when ladder points are on the line.
        .row.text-center
          .col-md-4
            span.fa-stack.fa-4x
              i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
              i.fa.fa-users.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
            h4.service-heading Leagues
            p.text-muted
              | Join with the people you play with most, prove who truely has the strongest game. Don't just play ... compete for the next rung up the ladder.
          .col-md-4
            span.fa-stack.fa-4x
              i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
              i.fa.fa-soccer-ball-o.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
            h4.service-heading Seasons
              .small (coming soon)
            p.text-muted
              | Don't get stuck playing with the same four people over and over, let foosnet.io schedule your season. See who comes out on top.
          .col-md-4
            span.fa-stack.fa-4x
              i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
              i.fa.fa-shield.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
            h4.service-heading Tournaments
              .small (coming soon)
            p.text-muted
              | For those days where you have to settle the score now, enlist your challengers and let foosnet.io manage the brackets. Best of luck.

    section#how-it-works
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12.text-center
            h2.section-heading How it works
            h3.section-subheading.text-muted It's simple, but not easy. Hone your skills and climb the ranks.
        .row
          .col-lg-12
            ul.timeline
              li
                .timeline-image
                  span.number 1
                .timeline-panel
                  .timeline-heading
                    h4 Register
                    h4.subheading Become a player
                  .timeline-body
                    p.text-muted
                      | Tell the world you are a fooser. Become a player and start building your name. Each game you play will alter your rating. It's the Elo system where winning games increases your rating, losing games loses you points.
              li.timeline-inverted
                .timeline-image
                  span.number 2
                .timeline-panel
                  .timeline-heading
                    h4 Play
                    h4.subheading Join a league
                  .timeline-body
                    p.text-muted
                      | Competing against yourself has it's limits. Join a league with the people you play with most. Challenge for the top of the ladder. Play in singles or in pairs. Don't have a league? Start your own!
              li
                .timeline-image
                  span.number 3
                .timeline-panel
                  .timeline-heading
                    h4 Compete
                    h4.subheading Make it a tournament
                  .timeline-body
                    p.text-muted
                      | Tensions running high in your league and some scores need to be settled now? Enter the proving grounds and duke it out in double or single elimination tournaments. Leave the brackets to us.
              li.timeline-inverted
                .timeline-image
                  h4
                    | Don't just
                    br
                    | play ...
                    br
                    | compete!

    section#contact
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12.text-center
            h2.section-heading Contact Us
            h3.section-subheading.text-muted Have questions? We always like hearing from you.
        .row
          .col-lg-12
            form#contactForm(name='sentMessage', novalidate='')
              .row
                .col-md-6
                  .form-group
                    input#name.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Your Name *', required='', data-validation-required-message='Please enter your name.')
                    p.help-block.text-danger
                  .form-group
                    input#email.form-control(type='email', placeholder='Your Email *', required='', data-validation-required-message='Please enter your email address.')
                    p.help-block.text-danger
                  .form-group
                    input#location.form-control(type='tel', placeholder='Your Location *', required='', data-validation-required-message='Please enter your location.')
                    p.help-block.text-danger
                .col-md-6
                  .form-group
                    textarea#message.form-control(placeholder='Your Message *', required='', data-validation-required-message='Please enter a message.')
                    p.help-block.text-danger
                .clearfix
                .col-lg-12.text-center
                  #success
                  button.btn.btn-xl(type='submit') Send Message
    footer
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-4
            span.copyright Copyright Â© foosnet.io 2015
          .col-md-4
            ul.list-inline.social-buttons
              li
                a(href='https://twitter.com/foosnetio', target="_blank")
                  i.fa.fa-twitter
              li
                a.github(href='https://github.com/burtonjc/foosnet.io', target="_blank")
                  i.fa.fa-github-alt
